  "title": "AB03 - Import/Export Shipping Officer (Sea & Air Freight) | Changi – Up to $3.5k",
  "description": "<p><strong>Freight Operation Executive (Sea & Air Freight)</strong></p><ul><li>Mon - Friday 8:30am to 5:30pm Saturday 8:30am to 12:30 pm </li><li>Working Location: Changi South</li><li>Salary : $2500 - $3500</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities </strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate and manage the logistics and shipping operations for both inbound and outbound freight, ensuring timely and efficient delivery</li><li>Assist in preparing and reviewing shipping documents, including airway bills, bills of lading, and other required import/export paperwork</li><li>Monitor and track shipments to ensure smooth transportation from origin to destination, updating clients and stakeholders as needed</li><li>Inspect cargo in the warehouse, ensuring proper storage, handling, and compliance with safety regulations</li><li>Perform data entry tasks related to shipment tracking, cargo details, and other logistics documentation</li><li>Support permit declarations and ensure compliance with customs regulations</li><li>Collaborate with freight forwarders, carriers, and internal teams to resolve any operational issues or delays</li><li>Provide support to both clients and internal teams, answering queries related to shipments, documentation, and logistics processes</li><li>Carry out any ad-hoc duties as required to support the logistics department and meet operational goals</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>With relevant working experience</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279<br /></p>",
